How to activate the Credit Card recurring charge?

In the mobilize events monthly plan, you can choose the Credit Card recurring charge.

This way, the payment method saves the data of your card and performs the payment
automatically every day X (x = expiration date of your subscription).

Activating the Credit Card recurring charge
  1. Open an invoice that is still pending (not yet paid)
  2. Fill in with your credit card data
  [image]
  3. Mark the field "Use this credidt card in future charges"

Done! Now the next payment will be made automatically and you will receive your
receipt via email.
